This repository contains files related to the LVRUG presentation
on November 4, 2014, whose purpose was to introduce the ggplot2
package. The files used during the presentation are 

* ggplot2shortForm.pres
* script.R

More detailed slides are in the file ggplot2Lecture.rpres and a
more complex set of ggplot2 scripts are in the file
scriptPostTalk.R. These are meant to be studied after the 
presentation.